-- Carstens Sees No Reason to Shift Monetary Policy, Reuters Says
-- B y   N a c h a   C a t t a n
-- 2012-02-22T20:26:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-22/carstens-sees-no-reason-to-shift-monetary-policy-reuters-says.html
Mexico ’s central bank Governor
Agustin Carstens said he sees “no reason” to change  monetary
policy  because the recent pickup in inflation has been due to
external and temporary factors, Reuters said.  There’s no evidence these factors are influencing “price
formation,” Carstens said in an interview with Reuters today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Nacha Cattan in Mexico City at 
